# CL-1: Regulatory Compliance
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All code touching sensitive, financial, or personal data

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Regulatory Compliance: Adherence to laws such as GDPR, HIPAA, PCI, and other jurisdictional requirements.
- Sensitive Data: Information requiring confidentiality or protection under law or policy.

ENFORCE: Every feature handling protected data must comply with applicable regulations before release.
PROHIBIT: Unauthorized data storage or transmission; non-compliant data handling.
ON VIOLATION: Halt skill execution → escalate to Legal/Compliance Skill.
